init_text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: learn how to be independent and responsible.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They should also learn how to be a good person and how to be a good citizen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If you are independent, you can do anything on your own.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can make your own decisions and you can solve problems by yourself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can also take care of yourself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Being responsible for your actions is also very important.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If you are responsible, you will not do anything that is bad for yourself or others.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will also be careful about your actions because you know that you have to take responsibility for them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Being a good person is also very important.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If you are a good person, you will not do anything that is bad for yourself or others.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will also be a good citizen because you will respect the rules and laws of the society and you will help others.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Being a good citizen is also very important.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: Being a good citizen is also very important.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: students should learn how to be independent and responsible for their actions in school.
